ot%3BHow%20come%20all%20the%20thieves%20have%20Modi%20as%20the%20common%20surname%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20put%20the%20conviction%20on%20hold%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20reason%20has%20been%20given%20by%20the%20trial%20judge%20for%20imposing%20maximum%20sentence.%20The%20order%20of%20conviction%20needs%20to%20be%20stayed%20pending%20final%20adjudication%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ramifications%20of%20disqualification%20not%20just%20affects%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20individual%20but%20also%20the%20electorate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judges%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20reprieve%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20has%20consistently%20refused%20to%20apologise%2C%20tweeted%2C%20%26quot%3BCome%20what%20may%2C%20my%20duty%20remains%20the%20same.%20Protect%20the%20idea%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20is%20on%20%26quot%3Bthin%20ice%26quot%3B%20given%20the%20number%20of%20cases%20against%20him.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20other%20criminal%20defamation%20cases%20pending%20against%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bthe%20high-profile%20case%20of%20mudslinging%20the%20venerable%20Veer%20Savarkar%26quot%3B%2C%20filed%20by%20the%20freedom%20fighter's%20family%2C%20tweeted%20BJP%20IT%20cell%20chief%20Amit%20Malviya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691332140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fv7tcc658_rahul-gandhi-ani-650_650x400_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-rahul-gandhi-return-to-parliament-tomorrow-all-eyes-on-speaker-4274344%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20papers%20for%20restoration%20of%20Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20are%20ready%20and%20all%20that%20remains%20is%20a%20sign-off%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker.%20This%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20done%20tomorrow%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C