e%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20derailment%20happened%20near%20Sahara%20railway%20station%20close%20to%20Nawabshah%20city%20in%20the%20southern%20Sindh%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEight%20coaches%20have%20derailed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohsin%20Syal%2C%20a%20railway%20official%2C%20told%20local%20HUM%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20railway%20minister%20said%20an%20emergency%20had%20been%20declared%20at%20local%20hospitals%20as%20doctors%20struggled%20to%20treat%20the%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20chaotic%20scenes%20at%20the%20Nawabshah%20Trauma%20Centre%20as%20ambulances%20and%20private%20cars%20ferried%20the%20injured%20for%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20man%20leapt%20from%20the%20back%20of%20an%20ambulance%20clutching%20a%20child%2C%20his%20clothes%20soaked%20in%20blood%2C%20while%20a%20woman%20moaned%20in%20pain%20as%20she%20was%20carried%20in%20on%20a%20stretcher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20what%20happened%2C%20we%20were%20just%20sitting%20inside%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20dazed%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20accident%20site%20outside%20Nawabshah%2C%20dozens%20of%20cars%2C%20tractors%2C%20rickshaws%20and%20motorcycles%20could%20be%20seen%20parked%20on%20a%20road%20that%20runs%20alongside%20the%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVolunteers%20were%20wading%20through%20a%20canal%20that%20separates%20the%20road%20from%20the%20railway%20line%20to%20help%2C%20and%20lifting%20the%20injured%20to%20get%20them%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelief%20train%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20passenger%20compartments%20were%20upright%20but%20off%20the%20tracks%2C%20while%20others%20lay%20on%20their%20side%2C%20mangled%20steel%20from%20the%20undercarriage%20twisted%20and%20buckled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20police%20official%20Younis%20Chandio%20told%20Geo%20News%20from%20the%20site%20that%20some%20passengers%20remained%20trapped%20in%20one%20carriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIjaz%20S