2C%20while%20companies%20can%20take%20risks%20in%20developing%20ambitious%20technology%20because%20they%20have%20NASA%20as%20a%20built-in%20customer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20baking%20in%20the%20commercial%20sector%20as%20part%20of%20their%20plans%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rosseau.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20created%20competition.%20It%20created%20incentives%20for%20companies%20to%20do%20things%20as%20reliably%20and%20also%20as%20cheaply%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20Rosseau%2C%20this%20model%20has%20started%20to%20bear%20fruit.%20Companies%20like%20Blue%20Origin%20and%20SpaceX%20likely%20wouldn't%20exist%20without%20NASA's%20ambition%20to%20go%20to%20the%20moon%2C%20he%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere's%20money%20in%20making%20future%20moon%20settlers%20comfortable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can't%20have%20mining%20on%20the%20moon%20without%20the%20proper%20infrastructure.%20And%20those%20looking%20to%20build%20it%20are%20starting%20to%20see%20money%20coming%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20to%20support%20long-term%20missions%20is%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20do%20cheap%20Earth-to-moon%20deliveries.%20NASA%20has%20been%20investing%20heavily%20in%20the%20development%20of%20uncrewed%20robotic%20landers%20that%20can%20deliver%20goods%20and%20services%20to%20the%20moon%20through%20its%20Commercial%20Lunar%20Payload%20Services%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-moon-rover-rocket-company-commercial-lunar-payload-services-clps-2020-6%5C%22%3ECLPS%3C%2Fa%3E%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPittsburg%20aerospace%20and%20robotics%20company%20Astrobotic%20Technology%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20players%20in%20the%20CLPS%20program.%20It%20landed%20a%20contract%20worth%20%24320%20million%20to%20deliver%20several%20payloads%20for%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20payload%2C%20the%20Volatiles%20Investigating%20Polar%20Exploration%20Rover%20or%20VIPER%2C%20is%20set%20to%20be%20delivered%20