-colony-2022-7%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNASA%2520is%2520developing%2520plans%2520to%2CMars%252C%2520an%2520expert%2520told%2520Insider.%5C%22%3Enuclear%20power%20reactors%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20moon.%20Lockheed%20Martin%20is%20one%20of%20the%20companies%20working%20on%20a%20concept%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENASA%20is%20also%20looking%20to%20develop%20appropriate%20moon-worthy%20rides.%20General%20Motors%20is%20teaming%20up%20with%20Lockheed%20Martin%20to%20develop%20a%20battery-powered%20lunar%20rover%20that%20could%20travel%20much%20further%20than%20those%20used%20in%20the%20Apollo%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20prerequisite%20for%20long-term%20settlement%20is%20navigation%20and%20communications.%20There's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fno-gps-on-moon-nasa-esa-artemis-plans-to-fix-2023-1%5C%22%3Eno%20GPS%20or%20Wi-Fi%20%3C%2Fa%3Earound%20or%20on%20the%20moon.%20That%20means%20missions%20rely%20on%20constant%20supervision%20from%20engineers%20on%20Earth%2C%20which%20will%20quickly%20become%20unsustainable%20as%20hundreds%20of%20missions%20are%20planned%20to%20be%20launched%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20fill%20that%20void%2C%20NASA%20awarded%20a%20%2414%20million%20contract%20to%20Nokia%20to%20deliver%20internet%20to%20the%20moon.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nokia.com%2Fabout-us%2Fnews%2Freleases%2F2023%2F02%2F27%2Fnokia-bell-labs-showcases-cutting-edge-research-on-lunar-networks-and-6g-at-mwc23%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F03%2F28%2Fnokia-set-to-launch-4g-internet-on-the-moon-later-this-year.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNokia%2520is%2520planning%2520to%2520launch%2Cneeds%2520of%2520future%2520space%2520missions.https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-nokia-4g-network-moon-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20firm%20aims%20to%20send%20a%204G%20network%20to%20the%20moon%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%202024.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nokia.com%2Fabout-us%2Fnews%2Freleases%2F2023%2F02%2F27%2Fnokia-bell-labs-showcases-cutting-edge-research-on-lunar-networks-and-6g-at-mwc23%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20artist's%20impression%20shows%20an%20astronaut%20sitting%20back%20while%20taking%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20Earth%20rising%20behind%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20moon%20with%20a%20smartphone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c52236cf07780019671e6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20future%20of%20moon%20exploration%20might%20look%20like%2C%20if%20phone%20networks%20are%20brought%20there.%3Cp%3Epeepo%2FNASA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EFly%20me%20to%20the%20moon%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20most%20lucrative%20part%20of%20the%20moon%20market%20by%20far%20is%20rocket%20development%2C%20said%20Kawade%2C%20who%20leads%20NSR's%20lunar-market%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENASA%20built%20its%20own%20system%20for%20its%20upcoming%20Artemis%20moon%20missions%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-how-nasa-built-sls-mega-rocket-artemis-moon-missions-2022-8%5C%22%3Ethe%20Space%20Launch%20System%3C%2Fa%3E%20(SLS)%20mega-rocket%20with%20its%20Orion%20spacecraft.%20But%20the%20agency%20has%20put%20the%20development%20of%20the%20mission's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-elon-musk-nasa-lunar-landing-astronauts-2021-4%5C%22%3Ehuman%20landing%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20(HLS)%2C%20which%20will%20bring%20astronauts%20from%20the%20moon's%20orbit%20to%20the%20lunar%20surface%2C%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20private%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk's%20SpaceX%20has%20been%20the%20frontrunner%20in%20the%20race%20to%20land%20this%20bid%2C%20gaining%20billion-dollar%20contracts%20to%20develop%20the%20HLS%20for%20NASA's%20Artemis%20III%