irst%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaddar%20has%20criticised%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20and%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20for%20not%20giving%20Dalits%20their%20due%20and%20instead%20bringing%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20feudalism%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20political%20leaders%20shared%20their%20condolences%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20love%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%20drove%20him%20to%20fight%20tirelessly%20for%20the%20marginalised.%20May%20his%20legacy%20continue%20to%20inspire%20us%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESaddened%20to%20hear%20about%20the%20demise%20of%20Shri%20Gummadi%20Vittal%20Rao%2C%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20poet%2C%20balladeer%20and%20fiery%20activist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20love%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%20drove%20him%20to%20fight%20tirelessly%20for%20the%20marginalised.%20May%20his%20legacy%20continue%20to%20inspire%20us%20all.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIlHcV6pObs%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FIlHcV6pObs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20(%40RahulGandhi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%2Fstatus%2F1688145227926925312%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20too%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20Gaddar%20from%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESaddened%20to%20hear%20about%20the%20passing%20of%20Shri%20Gummadi%20Vittal%20Rao%20garu%2C%20the%20iconic%20poet%20and%20relentless%20activist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20unwavering%20dedication%20to%20social%20causes%20and%20the%20fight%20for%20Tel