0decades%2C%20growing%20control%20over%20the%20private%20sector%20peaked%20in%20the%20zero-COVID%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20abrupt%20end%20to%20that%20policy%20won't%20revive%20growth%2C%20as%20it%20demonstrated%20the%20economy%20remains%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20party%20and%20its%20whims%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20%26quot%3Bself-insure%26quot%3B%20amid%20such%20uncertainty%2C%20people%20hoard%20cash%20and%20spend%20less%20on%20assets%20that%20aren't%20easily%20convertible%20to%20cash%2C%20such%20as%20cars%2C%20business%20equipment%2C%20and%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20condition%20is%20systemic%2C%20and%20the%20only%20reliable%20cure%E2%80%94credibly%20assuring%20ordinary%20Chinese%20people%20and%20companies%20that%20there%20are%20limits%20on%20the%20government's%20intrusion%20into%20economic%20life%E2%80%94cannot%20be%20delivered%2C%26quot%3B%20Posen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20any%20of%20Beijing's%20stimulus%20measures%20will%20not%20produce%20the%20intended%20results%20as%20consumers%20remain%20wary%20of%20further%20disruptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLow%20appetite%20for%20illiquid%20investment%20and%20low%20responsiveness%20to%20supportive%20macroeconomic%20policies%3A%20that%2C%20in%20a%20nutshell%2C%20is%20economic%20long%20COVID%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20already%20happening%3A%20though%20China's%20central%20bank%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fchina-economy-recovery-interest-rates-pboc-yuan-stock-market-news-2023-6%5C%22%3Ecut%20interest%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20stimulus%20efforts%20have%20been%20pledged%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20Politburo%20meeting%2C%20there's%20been%20little%20improvement%20in%20economic%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20West's%20growing%20tensions%20with%20Beijing%2C%20China's%20economic%20woes%20aren't%20necessarily%20good%20news%20for%20its%20rivals%20either%2C%20Posen%20sai