he%20long-term%20secular%20trend%20for%20US%20equity%20markets%20remains%20positive%20with%20an%20underlying%2016%20to%2018%20year%20cycle%20supportive%20of%20further%20upside%20into%20the%20mid%202030s%2C%20potentially%20to%20S%26amp%3BP%2014%2C000%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20forecast%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20to%20trade%20as%20high%20as%2014%2C000%20by%202034%20represents%20potential%20upside%20of%20209%25%20from%20current%20levels%2C%20or%20an%20average%20annualized%20gain%20of%20just%20under%2010%25%20over%20the%20next%2011%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Sluymer%2C%20these%20generational%20cycles%20have%20moved%20through%20periods%20of%20expansion%20and%20contraction%20that%20last%20nearly%20two%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221348%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22S%26amp%3BP%20500%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ca6d3b95fe1f0019dee3ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22733%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20past%20is%20a%20prologue%20for%20the%20future%2C%20the%20current%20secular%20uptrend%20could%20last%20into%20the%20early%20to%20mid%2020230s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-likely-bottom-october-fundstrat-new-bull-rally-sp500-2023-3%5C%22%3Efourth%20quarter%20of%202022%20represented%20a%20bottom%20for%20the%20cycle.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESluymer%20looked%20at%20a%20long-term%20chart%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20going%20all%20the%20way%20back%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-caused-the-great-depression%5C%22%3Ethe%20Great%20Depression%20in%201929.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Since%20then%2C%20there%20have%20only%20been%20two%20secular%20bull%20markets%2C%20with%20one%20occurring%20during%20the%201950s%20and%201960s%2C%20and%20another%20occurring%20during%20the%201980s%20and%201990s.%20Both%20generated%20total%20returns%20of%20about%202%2C300%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20current%20cycle%20generates%20a%20similar%20rally%20of%20%2B2000%25%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20could%20move%20toward%2014%2C000%20by%202034%20which%20is%20when%20we%20expect%20the%20current%2016%20to%2018%20year%20secular%20bull%20cycle%20to%20peak%2C%26quot%3B%20Sluymer%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20expansionary%20periods%20were%20countered%20with%20periods%20of%20contraction%2C%20during%20which%20stocks%20often%20move%20sideways%20over%20a%20period%20of%20nearly%20two%20decades.%20The%20last%20two%20contraction%20periods%20for%20the%20market%20occurred%20from%20the%20mid%201960s%20until%20the%20early%201980s%20and%20from%20the%20late%201990s%20to%20about%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20now%20and%202034%2C%20long-term%20oriented%20investors%20should%20lean%20bullish%20and%20view%20sell-offs%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20as%20opportunities%20to%20increase%20exposure%20to%20secular%20and%20cyclical%20growth%20stocks%2C%20including%20industrials%2C%20according%20to%20Sluymer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBottom%20line%3A%20We%20expect%20volatility%20to%20increase%20through%20earnings%20season%20into%20late%20Q3%20when%20seasonal%20weakness%20often%20develops.%20We%20recommend%20longer-term%20investors%20stay%20the%20course%20and%20remain%20optimistic%20about%20the%20evolving%20market%20cycle%20that%20bottomed%20in%20Q4%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221279%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22S%26amp%3BP%20500%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ca6cebce69770019845add%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-secular-bull-market-cyc