0the%20economy%20recovered%20from%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20benefitted%20from%20the%20rise%20in%20wages%20and%20the%20Great%20Resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20all%20part%20of%20how%20geriatric%20Gen%20Zers%20%E2%80%94%20the%20eldest%20group%20in%20the%20cohort%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D3e6a9f3381d82deaf39af0f8f01807b2ea86362dcd773da5b2515b5e64ed17d3%26postID%3D64cbbca9cfd91a08ec443a6c%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526isjs%253D1%2526jv%253D15.4.2-stackpath%2526sref%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.businessinsider.com%25252Ftypical-geriatric-gen-z-oldest-in-generation-work-life-school-4%2526url%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.insiderintelligence.com%25252Finsights%25252Fgeneration-z-facts%25252F%25253F_ga%25253D2.53950831.657270251.1690208115-793973004.1689966224%2526xs%253D1%2526xtz%253D240%2526xuuid%253D993a7ea34c6b6444febbbf2a7c5c90cf%2526xcust%253Dxid%25253Afr1690576859924aha%2526xjsf%253Dother_click__contextmenu%252520%25255B2%25255D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eborn%20between%201996%20and%202012%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%20disproportionately%20benefited%20from%20an%20unprecedented%20flow%20of%20money%20and%20jobs%20through%20a%20quirk%20of%20timing%2C%20as%20Gen%20Z%20economist%20and%20fellow%20class%20of%202019-er%20Joey%20Politano%20told%20me.%20Just%20because%20he'd%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20before%20the%20pandemic%20shut%20everything%20down%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20received%20all%20of%20this%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Politano%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20the%20class%20of%202019%20won%20the%20pandemic%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20class%20of%202019%20graduated%20into%20recession%20fears%2C%20but%20it%20was%20an%20economic%20downturn%20like%20none%20we've%20seen%20before%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPolitano%20technically%20graduated%20in%20fall%202018%2C%20but%20considers%20himself%20part%20of%20my%20coh