nces%2C%20Law%20and%20Justice%2C%20headed%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%2C%20said%20the%20representation%20of%20women%20personnel%20in%20the%20CAPFs%20and%20Assam%20Rifles%20is%203.76%20per%20cent%20as%20on%20September%2030%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Committee%20advocates%20that%20all%20necessary%20steps%20should%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20MHA%20(Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs)%20to%20encourage%20women%20to%20join%20the%20forces%20to%20the%20maximum%20possible%20extent.%20The%20major%20constraints%20preventing%20women%20from%20joining%20forces%20are%20the%20difficult%20terrains%20and%20the%20conditions%20in%20which%20they%20might%20have%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20its%20131st%20report%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BReview%20of%20Functioning%20of%20Recruitment%20Organisations%20of%20Government%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20a%20policy%20for%20women%20officers%20giving%20them%20soft%20postings%20and%20not%20subjecting%20them%20to%20extremely%20strenuous%20and%20difficult%20working%20conditions%20may%20be%20explored%2C%20unless%20required%20in%20extreme%20circumstances%20like%20a%20war%20or%20an%20armed%20rebellion%2C%20and%20that%20too%20when%20there%20is%20an%20absolute%20shortage%20of%20males%20who%20can%20be%20deployed%20by%20the%20forces%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Committee%20also%20recommends%20that%20some%20sort%20of%20reservation%20may%20also%20be%20given%20to%20transgenders.%20Steps%20may%20be%20taken%20to%20recruit%20transgenders%20as%20well%20so%20that%20they%20can%20be%20integrated%20well%20with%20mainstream%20society%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20%26quot%3Bimperative%20issue%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20minimal%20percentage%20of%20women%20in%20central%20forces%2C%20the%20panel%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20of%20today%2C%20only%203.65%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20vacancies%20for%20women%20have%20been%20filled%20till%20now.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20BSF%20(Border%20Security%20Force)%20and%20the%20SSB%20(Sashastra%20Seema%20Bal)%2C%20the%20representation%20of%20women%20is%20only%2014%20per%20cent%20to%2015%20per%20cent%2C%20in%20the%20CISF%20(Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force)%2C%20it%20is%206.35%20per%20cent%20and%20in%20the%20ITBP%20(Indo%20Tibetan%20Border%20Police)%2C%20it%20is%202.83%20per%20cent%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20there%20are%20certain%20constraints%20which%20are%20preventing%20women%20from%20joining%20the%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20panel%20said%20in%20its%20report%20tabled%20in%20Parliament%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20that%20there%20is%20no%20specific%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20the%20CAPFs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20in%20order%20to%20enhance%20the%20representation%20of%20women%20in%20CAPFs%2C%20in%202011%2C%20based%20on%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Empowerment%20of%20Women%2C%20directions%20were%20issued%20to%20bring%20the%20percentage%20of%20women%20in%20the%20forces%20to%205%20per%20cent%20within%203%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%2034%2C278%20women%20personnel%20posted%20in%20the%20CAPFs%20and%20AR%20as%20on%20September%2030%2C%202022.%20Of%20these%2C%201%2C894%20were%20in%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%207%2C470%20in%20BSF%2C%209%2C316%20in%20CISF%2C%209%2C427%20in%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%2C%202%2C514%20in%20ITBP%20and%203%2C657%20in%20SSB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20also%20said%20that%20it%20is%20paramount%20to%20recruit%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20youngsters%20from%20border%20districts%20and%20recommended%20a%20special%20drive%20for%20local%20youngsters%20of%26quot%3BChhattisgarh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20North%20Eastern%20states%20and%20Kashmir%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20should%20be%20ensured%20that%20the%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20reservation%20for%20areas%20affected%20by%20militancy%2FLWE%20(left%20wing%20extremism)%20and%2025%20per%20cent%20vacancies%20of%20border%20guarding%20forces%20allotted%20to%20border%20districts%20are%20fulfilled%20immediately%20so%20that%20the%20energy%20and%20talent%20of%20the%20youth%20of%20these%20areas%20are%20channelized%20and%20they%20do%20not%20deviate%20toward%20extremism%20and%20terrorism%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20also%20emphasised%20the%20filling%20up%20of%20all%20vacancies%20on%20mission%20mode%20in%20central%20armed%20police%20forces%20and%20Assam%20Rifles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%2083%2C127%20vacancies%20in%20the%20CAPFs%20and%20AR%20as%20on%20January%201%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20these%2C%201%2C666%20vacancies%20existed%20in%20AR%2C%2019%2C987%20in%20BSF%2C%2019%2C475%20in%20CISF%2C%2029%2C283%20in%20CRPF%2C%204%2C443%20in%20ITBP%2C%20and%208%2C273%20in%20SSB%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Committee%20recommends%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20robust%20mechanism%20to%20monitor%20how%20many%20people%20are%20retiring%20from%20forces%2C%20how%20many%20vacancies%20created%20and%20whether%20people%20have%20been%20appointed%20to%20the%20vacant%20posts%2C%20i.e.%20vacancies%20created%20should%20be%20filled%20regularly%20and%20backlogs%20to%20be%20avoided%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20departments%20should%20be%20strictly%20directed%20at%20all%20places%20that%20they%20send%20details%20of%20vacancies%20well%20in%20time%20to%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20and%20%26quot%3Bnot%20take%20years%20and%20years%20to%20send%20the%20details%20of%20vacancies%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691319000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2F7llqa12_women-army-650_625x300_20_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsoft-postings-for-women-transgender-quota-in-forces-parliamen