0the%20community%20at%20the%20refugee%20camp%20that%20they%20had%20a%20list%20of%20at%20least%2017%20locals%20they%20wanted%20to%20arrest%2C%20and%20had%20gotten%20only%20two%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Haryana%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fgurugram-news%2Frohingya-camps-bulldozed-as-suspects-identified-in-communal-violence-illegal-occupation-uncovered-in-nuh-s-tauru-area-101691146430860.html%5C%22%3Ebulldoze%20houses%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20shops%20belonging%20to%20locals%2C%20the%20Rohingya%20are%20also%20facing%20the%20same%20fate.%20In%20Nuh%E2%80%99s%20Tauru%2C%20shanties%20in%20Rohingya%20camps%20were%20also%20bulldozed%20on%20August%203.%20Local%20police%20have%20said%20that%20they%20have%20identified%20suspects%20related%20to%20the%20Nuh%20violence%20from%20among%20the%20Rohingya%20refugees%20who%20were%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20area%2C%20also%20claiming%20that%20these%20refugee%20camps%2C%20where%20the%20Rohingya%20have%20been%20living%20since%20years%2C%20were%20in%20fact%20encroachments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%80%98I%20Was%20Scared%2C%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Take%20a%20Chance%E2%80%99%3A%20Muslim%20Workers%20Flee%20After%20Violence%20in%20Gurugram's%20Badshahpur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fi-was-scared-didnt-take-a-chance-muslim-workers-flee-after-violence-in-gurugrams-badshahpur%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20Was%20Scared%2C%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Take%20a%20Chance%E2%80%99%3A%20Muslim%20Workers%20Flee%20After%20Violence%20in%20Gurugram%E2%80%99s%20Badshahpur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohd%20Abdullah%2C%20a%20Rohingya%20student%20who%20has%20left%20Nuh%2C%20feels%20that%20his%20community%20is%20cursed.%20%E2%80%9CWherever%20we%20go%2C%20just%20because%20we%20are%20Muslims%2C%20we%20are%20harassed%2C%E2%80%9D%2032-year-old%20Abdullah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20also%20added%20that%20the%20Rohingyas%20are%20scared%2C%20terrorised%20and%20feel%20utterly%20trapped%20in%20the%20situation.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20are%20we%20being%20made%20sacrificial%20goats%20in%20order%20to%20suffice%20the%20conscience%20of%20those%20holding%20the%20government%20accountable%3F%20And%20we%20are%20not%20concerned%20with%20any%20Hindu-Muslim%20issues%2C%20we%20are%20already%20refugees%2C%20why%20would%20any%20of%20us%20create%20trouble%20in%20a%20country%20giving%20us%20asylum%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20community%2C%20the%20Rohingya%20are%20largely%20Muslim%20refugees%20from%20Rakhine%20State%20who%20fled%20their%20homeland%20due%20to%20religious%20persecution%20by%20the%20Myanmar%20government%20in%202017.%20Over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fgurugram-news%2Frohingya-camps-bulldozed-as-suspects-identified-in-communal-violence-illegal-occupation-uncovered-in-nuh-s-tauru-area-101691146430860.html%5C%22%3E16%2C000%20UNHCR-certified%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rohingya%20refugees%20reside%20in%20India.%20The%20government%20estimates%20that%20at%20least%2040%2C000%20Rohingyas%20are%20present%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20snapped%20internet%2C%20restrictions%20on%20movement%20and%20being%20attacked%2C%20Rohingyas%20feel%20more%20helpless%20and%20devoid%20of%20rights%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20this%20helplessness%2C%20Sabber%20Kyaw%20Min%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20India-based%20Rohingya%20Human%20Rights%20Initiative%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20view%20of%20the%20Nuh%20violence%2C%20we%20as%20a%20community%20have%20come%20under%20fire%20again.%20Rohingya%20have%20been%20living%20in%20Nuh%20since%202014%2C%20and%20in%20all%20these%20years%2C%20not%20even%20once%20has%20even%20one%20of%20our%20community%20members%20committed%20a%20crime.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20that%20happened%2C%20Min%20explains%2C%20has%20not%20just%20shaken%20Indians%2C%20but%20the%20Rohingya%20too.%20%E2%80%9CBelieve%20me%2C%20when%20this%20happened%20in%20Nuh%2C%20all%20of%20us%20were%20mentally%20prepared%20to%20be%20used%20as%20scapegoats.%20We%20know%20how%20much%20groups%20like%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20detest%20us.%20If%20Indian%20Muslims%20are%20not%20safe%2C%20how%20can%20we%20Rohingya%20be%20safe%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Min.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocals%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20an%20approximate%202%2C000%20Rohingya%20lived%20in%20Nuh%2C%20and%20now%20they%20are%20even%20more%20vulnerable%20since%20they%20fear%20being%20targeted%20for%20the%20violence%20they%20were%20not%20a%20part%20of%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreceding%20these%20detentions%20and%20harassment%2C%20on%20July%2024%2C%20the%20Anti-Terrorist%20Squad%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%98raided%E2%80%99%20refugee%20Rohingya%20habitations%20in%20Mathura%2C%20Aligarh%2C%20Meerut%20and%20other%20locations%20in%20the%20state%20and%20arrested%20more%20than%2070%20persons%2C%20including%20women%20and%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20lawyers%20representing%20the%20detained%20refugees%2C%20they%20have%20been%20charged%20under%20sections%20of%20the%20Foreigners%20Act%2C%20despite%20the%20UNHCR%20identity%20cards%20they%20possessed.%20In%20Mathura%2C%20the%20UNHCR%20cards%20of%2030%20women%20and%20children%20left%20behind%20were%20also%20confiscated%20by%20the%20police.%20They%20face%20a%20food%20crisis%20as%20their%20families%E2%80%99%20sole%20male%20earners%20have%20been%20taken%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20on%20July%2019%2C%20more%20than%20270%20Rohingya%20refugees%20being%20held%20in%20a%20stadium%20turned%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98holding%20centre%E2%80%99%20in%20Jammu%20since%202021%20were%20fired%20upon%20and%20teargassed%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fafter-baby-dies-in-detention-centre-rohingya-family-brought-to-last-rites-in-handcuffs%5C%22%3Eallegedly%20causing%20the%20death%20of%20a%20baby%3C%2Fa%3