0biometric%20details%20of%20the%20refugees%20who%20have%20been%20taking%20shelter%20in%20these%20northeastern%20states%20after%20fleeing%20their%20strife-torn%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmha-pushes-manipur-mizoram-to-record-biometric-details-of-illegal-migrants%5C%22%3EMHA%20order%20on%20June%2022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20these%20states%20are%20to%20complete%20the%20process%20by%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20states%20were%20asked%20to%20lay%20out%20a%20plan%20and%20share%20it%20with%20the%20MHA%2C%20eventually%20officials%20from%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20had%20to%20visit%20the%20two%20states%20to%20train%20local%20officials%20on%20how%20to%20capture%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20August%205%20%3Cem%3EMizoram%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20the%20Zoramthanga%20government%20has%20informed%20the%20MHA%20that%20it%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20complete%20the%20task%20by%20the%20September%20deadline.%20The%20news%20report%20quoted%20state%20home%20minister%20H.%20Lalengmawia%20saying%20that%20the%20process%20was%20delayed%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20alteration%20of%20the%20format%20prepared%20by%20the%20MHA%20to%20suit%20the%20Myanmar%20refugees%20and%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20complete%20the%20data%20collection%20by%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20deadline%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20records%2C%20Mizoram%20has%2035%2C126%20Myanmar%20refugees%2C%20of%20whom%2015%2C589%20are%20taking%20shelter%20in%20relief%20camps%20while%2019%2C458%20have%20been%20either%20living%20in%20rented%20accommodation%20or%20with%20relatives.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-manipur-cms-stoking-of-ethnic-tensions-a-lesson-from-the-northeasts-history%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20earlier%20r%3C%2Fa%3Eeported%20that%20most%20of%20those%20staying%20in%20rented%20accommodation%20in%20Aizawl%20are%20political%20refugees%20and%20have%20been%20guarded%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Manipur%2C%20the%20process%20has%20begun%20early%20this%20week%20at%20the%20detention%20centre%20set%20up%20for%20the%20refugees%20by%20the%20state%20government%20near%20Sajjwa%20jail%20in%20Imphal.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.abplive.com%2Fnortheast%2Fmanipur-resumes-biometric-capture-campaign-for-illegal-myanmar-immigrants-following-mha-s-directives-1619293%5C%22%3ENews%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20put%20the%20Myanmar%20refugees%20currently%20residing%20in%20the%20detention%20centre%20at%20104%20which%20includes%2024%20men%2C%2074%20women%20and%20six%20children.%20They%20are%20said%20to%20have%20arrived%20in%20India%20after%20the%20military%20coup%20toppled%20the%20Aung%20San%20Suu%20Kyi%20government%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20kicking%20up%20an%20armed%20civil%20disobedience%20movement%20to%20restore%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20press%20statement%20by%20the%20state%20government%20on%20July%2029%20had%20said%20that%20the%20process%20of%20identifying%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20migrants%E2%80%9D%20would%20be%20carried%20out%20in%20all%20districts.%20Joint%20secretary%20at%20the%20state%20home%20department%2C%20Peter%20Salam%2C%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fnorth-east-india%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-starts-capturing-biometric-data-of-illegal-immigrants-from-myanmar-8866925%2F%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20district%20heads%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20identify%20%E2%80%9Call%20illegal%20migrants%E2%80%9D%20under%20their%20respective%20jurisdictions.%20He%20said%20over%202%2C500%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%20had%20been%20identified%20thus%20far%2C%20of%20whom%20Naga-dominated%20Chandel%20district%20had%20the%20highest%20at%20around%201%2C050.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20reacting%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20number%20in%20Chandel%2C%20the%20influential%20civil%20society%20group%20(CSO)%20United%20Naga%20Council%20(UNC)%20had%20said%20there%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Curgent%20need%E2%80%9D%20to%20update%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20in%20the%20state.%20Accusing%20the%20MHA%20of%20facilitating%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinflux%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20UNC%20in%20a%20press%20statement%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20alarming%20to%20learn%20the%20fresh%20influx%20of%20illegal%20immigrant%2C%20Myanmarese%20nationals%20along%20the%20Indo-Myanmar%20border%20in%20Chandel%20district%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20718%20persons%20in%20just%20a%20day%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report%20of%20Assam%20Rifles%2029%20sector%2C%20dated%20July%2023%2C%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20the%20UNC%2C%20several%20powerful%20Meitei%20CSOs%20have%20demanded%20a%20stop%20to%20the%20inflow%20of%20refugees%20from%20across%20the%20international%20border.%20During%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20of%20the%20Meitei%20community%20with%20the%20Kuki%20community%20which%20share%20ethnic%20affinities%20with%20the%20Chin%20people%20of%20Myanmar%2C%20not%20just%20the%20Meitei%20CSOs%20but%20the%20state%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20also%20accused%20them%20of%20harbouring%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%20from%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%201%2C600-km-long%20international%20border%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20Manipur%20shares%20390%20km%20while%20500%20km%20are%20along%20Mizoram.%20The%20border%20is%20porous%20as%20India%20has%20a%20free%20movement%20regime%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20which%20permits%20people%20residing%20on%20either%20side%20to%20travel%2017%20km%20on%20both%20sides%20without%20visa%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Nagaland%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20also%20share%20border%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20the%20arrival%20of%20refugees%20has%20been%20noted%20officially%20only%20in%20Manipur%20and%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691313825000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A