C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20surprising%20move%2C%20China%20has%20heavily%20come%20down%20on%20Russia%20for%20allegedly%20not%20letting%20Chinese%20citizens%20enter%20the%20country.%20In%20a%20statement%20on%20Friday%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%20called%20this%20move%20of%20the%20Russian%20authorities%20%E2%80%9Cbrutal%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-08-04%2Fchina-embassy-rips-brutal-russia-border-incident-in-rare-move%23xj4y7vzkg%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRussia%E2%80%99s%20brutal%20and%20excessive%20law-enforcement%20activities%20in%20this%20incident%20have%20seriously%20violated%20the%20legitimate%20rights%20and%20interests%20of%20the%20Chinese%20citizens%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20said%2C%20quoting%20the%20embassy%E2%80%99s%20post%20on%20Friday%20on%20WeChat%2C%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20used%20in%20China%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fchinas-embassy-russia-criticises-treatment-citizens-border-2023-08-05%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EReuters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20regarding%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20five%20Chinese%20citizens%20were%20trying%20to%20enter%20Russia%20via%20Kazakhstan%20late%20last%20month.%20They%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20enter%20after%20four%20hours%20of%20questioning%20and%20their%20visas%20were%20cancelled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20said%20that%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%20officials%20%E2%80%9Cmade%20representation%E2%80%9D%20to%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20Foreign%20Ministry%2C%20Federal%20Security%20Bureau%20and%20Federal%20Border%20Guard%20Service%20after%20a%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20surfaced.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20goes%20against%20the%20big%20picture%20of%20Sino-Russian%20friendship%20and%20the%20growing%20trend%20of%20friendly%20people-to-people%20exchanges%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Equoted%20the%20Chinese%20statement%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20standoff%20comes%20after%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20had%20last%20year%20proclaimed%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Cno%20limits%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20friendship%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20China%20has%20refused%20to%20condemn%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20war%20against%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20bilateral%20relations%20the%20countries%20have%20not%20seen%20a%20change.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20now%2C%20China%20has%20demanded%20answers%20from%20Russia%20on%20this%20incident.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20about%20the%20Chinese%20statement%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20language%20used%20in%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%E2%80%99s%20post%20is%20more%20aligned%20with%20what%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20diplomats%20reserve%20for%20protests%20against%20Western%20nations.%20The%20post%20demanded%20Russia%20explain%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20take%20active%20measures%20to%20eliminate%20the%20bad%20influence%2C%20and%20ensure%20that%20similar%20incidents%20will%20not%20recur%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chinese%20statement%20posted%20on%20WeChat%20was%20also%20quoted%20as%20saying%20that%20Russia%20needed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cconduct%20a%20further%20investigation%20into%20the%20excessive%20law%20enforcement%20activities%20by%20border%20guards%20and%20provide%20the%20Chinese%20side%20a%20satisfactory%20answer%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691310614000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F06132218%2FVladimir_Putin_met_with_Xi_Jinping_in_advance_of_2022_Beijing_Winter_Olympics_1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchina-slams-russia-for-alleged-mistreatment-of-citizens-at-border-demands-probe%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20Chinese%20citizens%20were%20allegedly%20stopped%20from%20entering%20Russia%20last%20month%20after%20hours%20of%20questioning%2C%20and%20their%20visas%20were%20cancelled.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchina-slams-russia-for-alleged-mistreatment-of-citizens-at-border-demands-probe%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20Sonam's%20Rs%20173%20crore%20mansion!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691310579000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102470676%2Cimgsize-114878.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdid-you-know-sonam-kapoor-and-anand-ahuja-own-a-luxurious-rs-173-crore-mansion-in-delhi-read-details%2Farticleshow%2F102470065.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102470065.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESonam%20Kapoor%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20OTT%20movie%20'Blind'%2C%20wherein%20she%20essayed%20the%20role%20of%20visually%20challenged%20person.%20She%20had%20taken%20two%20years%20off%20for%20pregnancy%20and%20has%20now%20signed%20two%20new%20projects.%20Sonam%20Kapoor%20will%20be%20seen%20in%20a%20web%20series%20and%20a%20movie.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdid-you-know-sonam-kapoor-and-anand-ahuja-own-a-luxurious-rs-173-crore-mansion-in-delhi-read-details%2Farticleshow%2F102470065.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20Path%3A%20Keep%20Your%20Friends%20Close%2C%20But%20the%20BJP%20Closer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F02145748%2FFL4fXEaWQAQau0B-e1646213553285.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20sudden%2C%20the%20announcement%20by%20the%20Naveen%20Patnaik-led%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20to%20support%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%20on%20two%20key%20issues%20in%20the%20Parliament%20should%20not%20surprise%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20announcing%20its%20twin%20decisions%20%E2%80%93%20to%20vote%20against%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20tabled%20by%20the%20opposition%20against%20Modi%2C%20and%20to%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20push%20to%20pass%20the%20Delhi%20services%20bill%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Odisha%20patriarch%20has%20given%20yet%20more%20proof%20of%20the%20political%20pragmatism%20that%20his%20party%20regularly%20practises%20to%20near%20perfection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20to%20be%20ideologically%20neutral%2C%20Patnaik%20has%20always%20been%20a%20shrewd%20political%20operator.%20And%20in%20rallying%20behind%20Modi%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20Parliament%20less%20than%20a%20year%20ahead%20of%20the%20next%20general%20elections%2C%20he%20has%20simply%20ensured%20that%20his%20long%20uninterrupted%20reign%20as%20the%20Odisha%20chief%20minister%20continues%2C%20minus%20any%20serious%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20big%20political%20decisions%20are%20taken%20in%20a%20vacuum%2C%20and%20it%20can%20be%20safely%20presumed%20that%20the%20decision%20by%20the%20BJD%20%E2%80%93%20long%20suspected%20to%20be%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20B-team%20%E2%80%93%20to%20extend%20support%20earlier%20this%20week%20came%20only%20after%20intense%20consultations%20and%20calculations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20could%20they%20be%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOdisha%20holds%20simultaneous%20elections%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20state%20assembly.%20In%202024%2C%20the%20state%20would%20elect%2021%20new%20members%20of%20parliament%20and%20vote%20to%20elect%20a%20new%20state%20government.%20It%20therefore%20gets%20more%20important%20for%20Patnaik%20who%20is%20eyeing%20another%20chief%20ministerial%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20has%20never%20shown%20any%20interest%20in%20assuming%20a%20larger%20role%20at%20the%20national%20level%20%E2%80%93%20unlike%20Modi%20or%20even%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20or%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Nitish%20Kumar%20%E2%80%93%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20politics%20has%20largely%20revolved%20around%20preserving%20his%20own%20position%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%20For%20him%2C%20winning%20parliamentary%20seats%20is%20welcome%2C%20but%20only%20incidental.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20clearly%20being%20his%20priority%2C%20the%20BJD%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20support%20Modi%20in%20parliament%20serves%20his%20immediate%20political%20interest.%20It%20might%20have%20reinforced%20popular%20suspicion%20of%20BJD%20being%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20B-team%2C%20but%20the%20damage%20it%20does%20to%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20credibility%20as%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20principal%20opposition%20party%20is%20significantly%20more.%20In%20popular%20perception%20%E2%80%93%20as%20reflected%20in%20opinion%20being%20currently%20voiced%20on%20social%20media%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%20is%20non-serious%20about%20unseating%20Patnaik%20and%20is%20covertly%20in%20collusion%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20awkward%20for%20both%20parties%2C%20the%20unwritten%20proximity%20between%20the%20two%20promises%20political%20dividends%20for%20both.%20Patnaik%20remains%20popular%20and%20prospects%20of%20him%20being%20voted%20out%20next%20year%20look%20remote.%20An%20enfeebled%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20its%20credibility%20as%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20main%20opposition%20compromised%20and%20its%20cadre%20confused%20%E2%80%93%20makes%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20continuity%20as%20chief%20minister%20more%20certain.%20For%20all%20practical%20purposes%2C%20it%20could%20well%20be%20a%20friendly%20contest%20in%20Odisha%20the%20next%20time%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20too%20stands%20to%20gain.%20It%20is%20likely%20that%20the%20party%20has%20read%20the%20popular%20mood%20in%20Odisha%20and%20has%20come%20to%20accept%20that%20it%20has%20little%20realistic%20chance%20of%20defeating%20Patnaik.%20It%20has%20therefore%20set%20its%20sight%20on%20post-2024%20results%20with%20Lok%20Sabha%20numbers%20in%20mind.%20Should%20it%20tally%20decline%20%E2%80%93%20as%20predicted%20by%20some%20political%20pundits%20%E2%80%93%20it%20would%20need%20to%20compensate%20for%20them.%20Patnaik%20with%20his%20MPs%20would%20come%20in%20handy%20then%20to%20ensure%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20majority%20and%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20continuation%20in%20power.%20To%20give%20up%20on%20its%20ambitions%20in%20Odisha%20would%20only%20be%20a%20small%20price%20to%20be%20paid%20for%20achieving%20its%20larger%20political%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20which%20way%2C%20this%20suits%20Patnaik.%20Though%20professing%20to%20be%20equidistant%20from%20polarising%20political%20combinations%20such%20as%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20and%20the%20newly%20formed%20INDIA%2C%20Patnaik%20has%20always%20sided%20with%20whoever%20happened%20to%20be%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20%E2%80%93%20right%20from%20AB%20Vajpayee%20to%20Manmohan%20Singh%20to%20Modi.%20Free%20of%20national%20ambitions%2C%20he%20had%20no%20political%20compulsion%20to%20oppose%20anyone.%20But%20being%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20one%20in%20power%20had%20benefits%3A%20it%20meant%20no%20CBI%20and%20ED%20and%20a%20relatively%20free%20run%20in%20his%20home%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Patnaik%20prefers%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%98covert%E2%80%99%20ally%20without%20giving%20up%20on%20his%20pretension%20of%20not%20being%20for%20or%20against%20any%20political%20group%20makes%20perfect%20sense.%20Joining%20the%20opposition%20ranks%20would%20invite%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20wrath.%20And%20officially%20siding%20with%20the%20BJP%20would%20open%20up%20the%20opposition%20space%20in%20Odisha%20for%20parties%20such%20as%20the%20Congress.%20He%20instead%20favours%20having%20a%20party%20he%20can%20influence%20as%20his%20principal%20opposition.%20To%20keep%20friends%20close%2C%20but%20enemies%20like%20the%20BJP%20closer%20seem%20to%20be%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20guiding%20principle.%20And%20he%20has%20been%20very%20successful%20at%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERuben%20Banerjee%20is%20the%20former%20Editor-in-Chief%20of%20Outlook%2C%20and%20the%20author%20of%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fem%3ENaveen%20Patnaik%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691308900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F02145748%2FFL4fXEaWQAQau0B-e1646213553285.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-naveen-patnaik-path-keep-your-friends-close-but-the-bjp-closer%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20rallying%20behind%20Modi%20less%20than%20a%20year%20ahead%20of%20the%20next%20general%20elections%2C%20Patnaik%20has%20ensured%20that%20his%20reign%20in%20Odisha%20continues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-naveen-patnaik-path-keep-your-friends-close-but-the-bjp-closer%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Five%20best-selling%20two-wheeler%20companies%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691308819000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fthumb%2Fmsid-102469918%2Cwidth-1070%2Cheight-580%2Cimgsize-1408646%2Cresizemode-75%2Coverlay-toi_sw%2Cpt-32%2Cy_pad-40%2Fphoto.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2