ry%2C%20and%20had%20to%20spend%20a%20large%20sum%20of%20money%20to%20cover%20the%20expenses%20of%20the%20shoot.%20They%20also%20alleged%20that%20they%20have%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20the%20makers%20who%20threatened%20them%20to%20take%20it%20back%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20had%20courted%20controversy%20since%20it%20bagged%20the%20Oscar%20as%20viewers%20were%20quick%20to%20point%20out%20the%20power%20dynamic%20between%20the%20filmmakers%20and%20the%20community%20they%20chose%20as%20subjects%20as%20well%20as%20the%20lack%20of%20this%20contextualisation%20in%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESikhya%20Entertainment%20and%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20director%20Kartiki%20Gonsalves%20have%20responded%20to%20the%20allegations.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20goal%20in%20creating%20The%20Elephant%20Whisperers%20has%20always%20been%20to%20highlight%20elephant%20conservation%2C%20the%20tremendous%20efforts%20of%20the%20Forest%20Department%20and%20its%20mahouts%20Bomman%20and%20Bellie.%20Since%20its%20launch%2C%20the%20documentary%20has%20raised%20awareness%20of%20the%20cause%20and%20had%20a%20real%20impact%20on%20the%20Mahouts%20and%20Cavadis%20community.%20Our%20honourable%20chief%20minister%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20MK%20Stalin%2C%20has%20made%20donations%20towards%20assisting%20the%2091%20Mahouts%20and%20Cavadis%20who%20look%20after%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20elephants%2C%20constructing%20eco-friendly%20houses%20for%20the%20caretakers%20and%20developing%20an%20Elephant%20Camp%20in%20the%20Anamalai%20Tiger%20Reserve%2C%E2%80%9D%20their%20statement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fentertainment%2Fthe-elephant-whisperers-bomman-and-bellie-allege-exploitation-by-docu-makers-kartiki-gonsalves-calls-claims-untrue%2Farticle67161291.ece%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fentertainment%2Fthe-elephant-whisperers-bomman-and-bellie-allege-exploitation-by-docu-mak