com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Faug%2F05%2Fmirwaiz-a-free-mannot-under-detention-jammu-and-kashmir-lt-governor-manoj-sinha-2602250.html%5C%22%3Etold%20a%20national%20daily%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hurriyat%2C%20however%2C%20rejected%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20claims%2C%20again.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20ironic%20is%20that%20the%20state%20authorities%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20deny%20this%20(house%20arrest%20of%20Mirwaiz)%20and%20say%20he%20is%20free%20while%20a%20police%20and%20paramilitary%20contingent%20remains%20permanently%20stationed%20outside%20his%20house%20disallowing%20him%20from%20leaving%20it%20(sic)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Hurriyat%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20tried%20to%20meet%20the%20Hurriyat%20leader%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Srinagar%E2%80%99s%20Nigeen%20locality.%20However%2C%20the%20police%20and%20paramilitary%20forces%20deployed%20at%20the%20main%20gate%20refused%20to%20give%20access%20to%20the%20residence.%20Authorities%20have%20not%20specified%20the%20charges%20under%20which%20Mirwaiz%20has%20been%20detained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F07175446%2FMirwaiz_Umar-Farooq_-3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F07175446%2FMirwaiz_Umar-Farooq_-3.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F07175446%2FMirwaiz_Umar-Farooq_-3-300x217.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F07175446%2FMirwaiz_Umar-Farooq_-3-1024x740.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-612392%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22867%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMirwaiz%20Umar%20Farooq.%20Photo%3A%20Files%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmirwaiz-umar-farooq-four-other-kashmiri-leaders-sign-bonds-to-secure-release%2Farticle29462227.ece%5C%22%3Ea%20report%20claimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Mirwaiz%20had%20signed%20a%20bond%20to%20secure%20his%20release%20from%20house%20arrest%20along%20with%20two%20leaders%20from%20the%20National%20Conference%20and%20one%20leader%20each%20from%20the%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%20and%20Peoples%20Conference.%20The%20bond%2C%20reportedly%20signed%20under%20Section%20107%20of%20the%20CrPC%2C%20prohibited%20Mirwaiz%20and%20others%20from%20making%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20speeches%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMirwaiz%20had%20rejected%20the%20claim%20that%20he%20signed%20a%20bond%20to%20secure%20his%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20Mirwaiz%20has%20consistently%20criticised%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies%20and%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20Kashmir%20in%20his%20media%20statements%2C%20while%20calling%20for%20the%20release%20of%20the%20prisoners%20who%20were%20arrested%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20are%20presently%20languishing%20in%20different%20jails%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hurriyat%20said%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20continue%20to%20safeguard%20the%20rights%20and%20interests%20of%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20advocate%20dialogue%2C%20good%20neighbourly%20relations%2C%20peaceful%20coexistence%20and%20brotherhood%20among%20communities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJailing%20Kashmiri%20political%20leadership%2C%20cadres%2C%20activists%20%E2%80%A6..%20as%20a%20means%20of%20establishing%20peace%20and%20an%20approach%20to%20problem%20solving%20is%20the%20way%20of%20the%20current%20dispensation.%20What%20is%20to%20be%20seen%20is%20how%20long%20this%20approach%20is%20followed%20and%20implemented%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Hurriyat%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20influential%20separatist%20leader%2C%20Mirwaiz%20was%20also%20part%20of%20a%20delegation%20of%20the%20moderate%20Hurriyat%20leaders%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20bilateral%20talks%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20over%20the%20Kashmir%20issue.%20The%20delegation%20also%20met%20the%20then%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20and%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20L%20.K.%20Advani%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talks%20suffered%20a%20setback%20in%202009%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20and%2C%20back%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20moderates%20were%20grilled%20by%20the%20hawks%20in%20the%20Hurriyat%20led%20by%20Syed%20Ali%20Geelani%20for%20participating%20in%20India-Pakistan%20rapprochement%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20Kashmir%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%20beefed%20up%20on%20August%205%2C%20political%20leaders%20under%20%E2%80%98house%20arrest%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20was%20beefed%20up%20across%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20on%20Saturday%2C%20which%20marked%20the%20fourth%20anniversary%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20on%20August%205%2C%202019.%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20president%20and%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20Chief%20Minister%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20put%20under%20house%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PDP%20chief%20had%20planned%20to%20lead%20a%20rally%20against%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370.%20But%20the%20party%20said%20that%20besides%20Mehbooba%2C%20some%20of%20its%20senior%20leaders%2C%20such%20as%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20ministers%20Naeem%20Akhtar%20and%20A.R.%20Veeri%20among%20others%2C%20were%20either%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%20or%20detained%20at%20police%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Conference%20led%20by%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20also%20alleged%20that%20its%20party%20office%20in%20Srinagar%20was%20%E2%80%9Clocked%20down%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20authorities.%E2%80%9CTrue%20to%20form%20and%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20clampdown%20on%20mainstream%20democratic%20activities%20organised%20by%20parties%20opposed%20to%205th%20Aug%202019%2C%20the%20JKNC%20office%20has%20been%20sealed%20by%20the%20police.%20No%20one%20is%20being%20allowed%20in%20or%20out%20of%20the%20office%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20party%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%2C%20however%2C%20allowed%20a%20BJP%20rally%20in%20Srinagar%20for%20celebrating%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%2C%20while%20a%20public%20programme%20was%20also%20organised%20by%20the%20party%20in%20the%20capital%20city.%C2%A0The%20party%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20has%20%E2%80%9Cbrought%20peace%2C%20development%20and%20prosperity%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Conference%20vice-president%20and%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20had%20also%20demanded%20the%20release%20of%20Mirwaiz%20after%20authorities%20eased%20some%20restrictions%20on%20the%20Muharram%20processions%20in%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMirwaiz%20Umar%20Farooq%20is%20a%20religious%20leader%20and%20he%20should%20be%20released.%20Prayers%20should%20be%20allowed%20at%20Jamia%20Masjid%20without%20any%20curbs%20and%20Eid%20prayer%20should%20be%20allowed%20at%20Eidgah%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abdullah%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnjuman%20Auqaf%20Jamia%20Masjid%2C%20the%20managing%20body%20of%20the%20mosque%20where%20Mirwaiz%20led%20Friday%20prayers%2C%20also%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday%20demanding%20his%20release.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20all%20other%20religious%20activities%20are%20permitted%20and%20in%20fact%20facilitated%20by%20the%20authorities%2C%20it%20is%20openly%20discriminatory%20that%20he%20(Mirwaiz)%20is%20barred%20from%20his%20duties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20statement%2C%20the%20Hurriyat%20said%20that%20Mirwaiz%20has%20%E2%80%9Calways%20advocated%20and%20led