2F102455372.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENASA%20has%20succeeded%20in%20re-establishing%20full%20contact%20with%20Voyager%202%20by%20using%20its%20highest-power%20transmitter%20to%20send%20an%20%26quot%3Binterstellar%20shout%26quot%3B%20that%20righted%20the%20distant%20probe's%20antenna%20orientation%2C%20the%20space%20agency%20said%20Friday.%20Launched%20in%201977%20to%20explore%20the%20outer%20planets%20and%20serve%20as%20a%20beacon%20of%20humanity%20to%20the%20wider%20universe%2C%20it%20is%20currently%20more%20than%2012.3%20billion%20miles%20(19.9%20billion%20kilometers)%20from%20our%20planet%20--%20well%20beyond%20the%20solar%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnasa-back-in-touch-with-voyager-2-after-interstellar-shout%2Farticleshow%2F102455372.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnasa-back-in-touch-with-voyager-2-after-interstellar-shout%2Famp_articleshow%2F102455372.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnasa-back-in-touch-with-voyager-2-after-interstellar-shout%2Famp_articleshow%2F102455372.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ninth%20Cheetah%20in%20Kuno%20Died%20Due%20to%20Maggot%20Infection%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F27113722%2Farmand-kamffer-mhbXY-RcLZA-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Dhatri%2C%20the%20female%20cheetah%20that%20authorities%20found%20dead%20in%20the%20wild%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20on%20August%202%2C%20died%20due%20to%20myiasis%20or%20maggot%20infection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Cheetah%20Conservation%20Fund%20(CCF)%2C%20which%20assists%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20said%20this%20in%20a%20series%20of%20tweets%20on%20August%203.%20Dhatri%20is%20the%20third%20cheetah%20to%20die%20of%20such%20an%20infection%20in%20the%20Park.%20Post-mortem%20reports%20found%20that%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20of%20cheetahs%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%20on%20July%2011%20and%2014%20were%20due%20to%20septicaemia.%20The%20animals%20had%20maggot-infested%20wounds%2C%20per%20reports.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMaggot%20infestation%2C%20again%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCCFCheetah%2Fstatus%2F1687116755548995584%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eseries%20of%20tweets%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20August%203%2C%20the%20Cheetah%20Conservation%20Fund%20(CCF)%20which%20assists%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20said%20that%20a%20post-mortem%20revealed%20that%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fninth-cheetah-dies-in-kuno-national-park%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eninth%20cheetah%20that%20was%20found%20dead%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Kuno%20on%20August%202%20died%20due%20to%20myiasis%2C%20or%20infection%20caused%20by%20fly%20larvae%20(maggots).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECCF%E2%80%99s%20Conservation%20Release%20programme%20manager%2C%20Barth%20Balli%2C%20spent%2010%20days%20tracking%20Dhatri%2C%20a%20female%20from%20Namibia%2C%20to%20get%20close%20enough%20to%20capture%20her%2C%20the%20tweets%20said.%20Though%20he%20could%20not%20capture%20her%20he%20saw%20that%20she%20had%20successfully%20hunted%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20vet%20team%2C%20CCF%20conducted%20a%20post-mortem%20examination.%20The%20cause%20of%20death%20was%20infection%20due%20to%20maggot%20infestation%20(myiasis)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20tweet%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20same%20cause%20of%20death%20for%20two%20male%20cheetahs%20and%20the%20reason%20why%20we%20were%20tracking%20Dhatri%20for%20recapture.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CCF%20added%20that%20authorities%20have%20removed%20collars%20from%20all%20cheetahs%20in%20captivity%20while%20they%20%E2%80%9Cdevelop%20and%20test%20a%20better%20collar%20material%20for%20their%20monitoring%20devices%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20male%20cheetahs%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%E2%80%99s%20deaths%20on%20July%2011%20and%2014%2C%20post-mortem%20reports%20revealed%20that%20the%20animals%20had%20died%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctraumatic%20shock%E2%80%9D%20set%20on%20by%20septicaemia.%20Per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbhopal%2Fmore-cheetahs-at-kuno-have-neck-wounds-collars-blamed%2Farticleshow%2F101840088.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20animals%20had%20maggot-infested%20wounds.%20Experts%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20infections%20were%20caused%20by%20the%20radio%20collars%20on%20the%20animals%E2%80%99%20necks.%20However%2C%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20(NTCA)%20which%20implements%20Project%20Cheetah%20denied%20this%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fauthorities-say-recent-cheetah-deaths-due-to-natural-causes-mp-chief-wildlife-warden-transferred%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20all%20deaths%20have%20been%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20authorities%20have%20been%20capturing%20all%20cheetahs%20in%20the%20wild%20in%20Kuno%20to%20monitor%20their%20health.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20their%20tweet%2C%20the%20CCF%20said%20that%20fly%20eggs%20have%20a%20rapid%20incubation%20rate%20and%20the%20larvae%20%E2%80%9Care%20not%20easy%20to%20detect%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20quickly%20reach%20full%20growth%20in%20less%20than%20a%20couple%20%5Bof%5D%20days.%20Myiasis%20also%20occurs%20in%20humans%2C%20and%20is%20common%20in%20rural%20areas%20with%20tropical%20climates%20(India)%20or%20during%20rainy%20seasons%20in%20arid%20climates%20(Namibia).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAll%20in%20bomas%20doing%20well%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20Dhatri%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20there%20is%20only%20one%20more%20cheetah%20in%20the%20wild%20in%20Kuno.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETeams%20are%20working%20to%20bring%20back%20Nirva%2C%20a%20female%20from%20South%20Africa%2C%20for%20%E2%80%9Ccomprehensive%20health%20assessments%20and%20any%20necessary%20treatments%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20CCF%20said.%20It%20added%20that%20all%20the%20other%2014%20cheetahs%20at%20Kuno%20in%20pre-release%20bomas%20%E2%80%93%20seven%20males%2C%20six%20females%2C%20and%20a%20female%20cub%20%E2%80%93%20are%20%E2%80%9Chealthy%20and%20thriving%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20under%20regular%20observation%20by%20our%20expert%20team%20in%20Kuno%2C%E2%80%9D%20their%20tweet%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20priority%20is%20the%20well-being%20of%20these%20incredible%20animals%2C%20and%20their%20progress%20toward%20successful%20release%20into%20the%20wild%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20tweet%20also%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStudies%20conducted%20between%202004%20and%202018%20found%20high%20success%20rates%20%E2%80%93%20of%20between%2075-96%25%20%E2%80%93%20of%20%E2%80%9Cselected%20individuals%20in%20achieving%20independence%20post-release%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20claimed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%2020%20adult%20cheetahs%20that%20arrived%20in%20Kuno%20in%20September%202022%20and%20February%20this%20year%20as%20part%20of%20Project%20Cheetah%20%E2%80%93%20India%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20cheetah%20reintroduction%20programme%20%E2%80%93%20six%20have%20died%20due%20to%20various%20causes.%20Three%20of%20the%20four%20cubs%20born%20in%20the%20park%20have%20also%20died.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691244131000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F27113722%2Farmand-kamffer-mhbXY-RcLZA-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fninth-cheetah-in-kuno-died-due-to-maggot-infection%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dhatri%2C%20a%20female%20that%20was%20found%20dead%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20August%202%2C%20is%20the%20third%20cheetah%20to%20die%20of%20such%20an%20infection.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fninth-cheetah-in-kuno-died-due-to-maggot-infection%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Imran%20Khan%20accused%20Pakistan%20government%20of%20'dismantling%20democracy'%20before%20arrest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691243040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-imran-khan-arrest_6241239.jpg%3F20230805135858%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fformer-pakistan-pm-imran-khan-accused-government-of-dismantling-democracy-before-arrest-12934271%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20former%20prime%20minister%20Imran%20Khan%20said%20his%20party%20had%20faced%20unprecedented%20%26quot%3Bvictimisation%26quot%3B%20and%20accused%20the%20country's%20government%20of%20%26quot%3Bdismantling%20democracy%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20an%20interview%20before%20his%20latest%20arrest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A117%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fformer-pakistan-pm-imran-khan-accused-government-of-dismantling-democracy-before-arrest-12934271%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.amppr