he%20vote%20swung%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcaste-calculations-in-rajasthan-and-why-pilot-matters-in-30-seats-123060400306_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2018%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20election%20when%20Sachin%20Pilot%2C%20a%20Gujjar%20leader%2C%20was%20sent%20up%20by%20Congress.%20That%20said%2C%20there%20is%20anti-Congress%20sentiment%20in%20the%20group%20now%20with%20their%20leader%20being%20denied%20the%20top%20position%2C%20exacerbated%20by%20Pilot%E2%80%99s%20public%20and%20vocal%20unhappiness%20on%20the%20subject.%20Both%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20are%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20230710024918%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Frajput-rajasthan-bhairon-singh-shekhawat-bjp-congress-8623357%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ematch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20Rajput%20vote%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20Congress%20took%20a%20cool%20100%20seats%20of%20the%20available%20200%2C%20with%20BJP%20under%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20stopping%20at%2073.%20This%20time%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20different%20%E2%80%93%20opinion%20polls%20show%20the%20BJP%20firmly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-election-2023-opinion-poll-prediction-ashok-gehlot-sachin-pilot-vasundhara-raje-bjp-congress-seats-tally-prediction%2F3191506%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eahead%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20getting%20its%20infighting%20only%20recently%20under%20control%2C%20and%20an%20anticipated%20split%20of%20109-119%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%2078-88%20to%20Congress.%20If%20it%20came%20down%20to%20the%20line%2C%20it%20would%20be%20safer%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20alienate%20the%20Rajput%20vote%20over%20the%20Gujjar%2C%20but%20it%20would%20have%20ripple%20effects%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fbjp-overhauls-its-uttar-pradesh-unit%2Farticle66664913.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecultivating%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20representation%20within%20the%20Brahmin%2C%20Rajput%20and%20non-Yadav%20OBCs%20as%20they%20cannot%20afford%20absolutely%20any%20uncertainty%20for%202024.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESet%20one%20problem%20to%20solve%20another%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20would%20be%20extremely%20injudicious%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20ongoing%20Haryana%20riots%20have%20been%20deliberately%20manufactured%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20order%20to%20create%20conditions%20where%20unpleasant%20electoral%20outcomes%20can%20be%20avoided%20and%20a%20larger%20anti-Muslim%20threat%20can%20be%20mobilised%20to%20unite%20caste%20factionalism%20under%20the%20larger%20Hindutva%20umbrella.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20all%2C%20surely%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20used%20a%20larger%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpulwama-narendra-modi-bjp-2019-elections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esecurity%20threat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20a%20way%20of%20shifting%20the%20dial%20on%20an%20election%20before%3F%20It%20would%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20be%20flirting%20with%20outright%20sedition%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20creation%20of%20these%20conditions%20were%20a%20result%20of%20significant%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwatch-karan-thapar-satya-pal-malik-narendra-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esecurity%20lapses%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20made%20by%20the%20state%20despite%20prior%20knowledge%20that%20should%20have%20prohibited%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2010%2F10%20seats%20from%20Haryana%2C%20and%2024%2F25%20out%20of%20Rajasthan%20(with%20a%20single%20seat%20going