ave%20a%20lot%20riding%20on%20them%20in%20relation%20to%20how%202024%20will%20be%20perceived.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20took%20a%20significant%20hit%20with%20the%20loss%20of%20Karnataka.%20To%20lose%20Rajasthan%20electorally%20and%20now%20Haryana%20emotively%20would%20take%20what%20is%20currently%20a%20tight%20race%2C%20into%20an%20active%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrem%20Shankar%20Jha%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20has%20the%20BJP%20running%20nervous%2C%20given%20that%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20parties%20has%20created%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-democracy-survival-complacency%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emultiplier%20effect%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20their%20favour.%20According%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-the-electoral-math-of-india-vs-nda-4240701%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAmitabh%20Tiwari%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20their%20vote%20share%20has%20gone%20up%20by%2010%25%2C%20whereas%20the%20factionalism%20running%20rampant%20in%20the%20BJP%20allies%20has%20brought%20theirs%20down.%20Of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20current%20303%20seats%2C%20there%20is%20also%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-the-electoral-math-of-india-vs-nda-4240701%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eclose%20fight%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20taking%20place%20in%2045.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20the%2035%20seats%20between%20Haryana%20and%20Rajasthan%20suddenly%20start%20to%20look%20a%20lot%20more%20important.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20then%2C%20there%20was%20a%20riot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20Haryana%20on%20fire%2C%20and%20a%20significant%20mobilisation%20of%20Hindutva%20militants%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20fake%20news%20factories%20amplifying%20narratives%20of%20Muslim%20violence%2C%20there%20is%20now%20a%20%E2%80%98bigger%20threat%E2%80%99%20than%20one%20of%20caste%20solidarity%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20has%20the%20wildfire%20momentum%20of%20the%20Rajput%20lobby%20been%20physically%20and%20digitally%20stopped%2C%20it%20will%20be%20unlikely%20to%20be%20revived%20given%20that%20Haryana%20will%20be%20tending%20to%20a%20different%20wound.%20It%20also%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20hurt%20that%20the%20party%20has%20been%20suffering%20from%20the%20optics%20of%20the%20Manipur%20gang%20rape%20viral%20video%2C%20which%20has%20now%20been%20neatly%20removed%20from%20the%20news%20cycle%20and%20replaced%20with%20bankable%20outrage%20and%20fury%20on%20the%20Haryana%20front.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20also%20refreshed%20the%20communal%20verve%20in%20the%20cow%20belt%2C%20where%20it%20has%20the%20most%20electoral%20returns%2C%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20kept%20fresh%20so%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20start%20to%20remember%20they%20are%20unemployed%2C%20paying%20Rs%20160-a-kilo%20for%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20watching%20their%20taxes%20line%20Ambani%20pockets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20question%20still%20rises%2C%20out%20of%20sheer%20disbelief%3A%20surely%20all%20this%20could%20not%20be%20related%20to%20a%20statue%20of%20a%20man%20from%20the%209th%20century%3F%20The%20answer%20to%20which%20is%20%E2%80%93%20how%20much%20would%20you%20be%20willing%20to%20risk%20to%20win%20the%202024%20election%2C%20when%20the%20alternative%20is%20just%20to%20have%20a%20nice%20riot%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691239222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10130903%2F640px-thumbnail.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Friots-and-wrong-communal-violence-raises-electoral-stakes-but-who-gains-from-polarisation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sur