around%20100%20toys%20so%20far.%20Each%20toy%20is%20usually%20priced%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%20800%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20depending%20on%20the%20work%20involved.%20They%20are%20also%20working%20on%20adding%20more%20categories.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20receive%20our%20toys%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-3-1690981932.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kirat%20hires%20people%20from%20his%20community%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20work%20opportunities%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-3-1690981932.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-3-1690981932-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-3-1690981932-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-3-1690981932-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-3-1690981932-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326117%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKirat%20hires%20the%20artisans%20from%20his%20community%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20work%20opportunities%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Zankla%20Studio%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20shares%20that%20the%20real%20test%20of%20the%20toys%20came%20when%20he%20received%20an%20order%20from%20a%2090-year-old%20woman%20from%20Mumbai.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20her%2090th%20birthday%20and%20she%20wanted%20to%20gift%20something%20to%20her%20friends.%20She%20had%20read%20about%20me%20and%20was%20curious%20to%20see%20the%20products.%20I%20was%20deligh