%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F72957%2Fanita-kaul-ias-rte-act-karnataka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Nali%20Kali%E2%80%99%20scheme%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhich%20means%20%E2%80%98joyful%20learning%E2%80%99%20in%20Kannada.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20classes%20are%20full%20of%20activities.%20Regular%20subjects%20are%20taught%20through%20games%2C%20songs%2C%20colourful%20charts%2C%20educational%20toys%2C%20game%20boards%2C%20dice%2C%20flashcards%2C%20and%20storytelling.%20We%20also%20conduct%20weekly%20dance%20activities%20and%20sports%20classes%20twice%20a%20week%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manimakalai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20time%2C%20several%20government%20schools%20approached%20us%20to%20adopt%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20multi-grade%20and%20multi-level%20education%20program%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2053-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Gubbachi%20has%20established%20two%20centres%20to%20implement%20the%20bridge%20learning%20programme%20and%20works%20with%20nine%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F171106%2Fbengaluru-govt-school-inspiring-hero-education-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egovernment%20schools%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20educate%20classes%201%E2%80%933%20through%20Nali%20Kali.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20that%20if%20we%20give%20these%20children%20a%20good%20foundation%2C%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20perform%20better%20in%20Class%204%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20they%20have%20associated%20with%20over%2060%20teachers%20to%20help%20them%20implement%20various%20programmes%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPromoting%20equitable%20learning%20for%20thousands%20for%20free%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20children%20above%2010%20years%20of%20age%20or%20above%2C%20Gubbachi%20first%20enrols%20them%20in%20brid