-hill-3-1690871491-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fpali-hill-3-1690871491-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fpali-hill-3-1690871491-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fpali-hill-3-1690871491-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325873%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EToday%20Pali%20Hill%20in%20Bandra%2C%20Mumbai%20is%20a%20sustainable%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhu%20elaborates%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20do%20considerable%20paperwork%20and%20convince%20BMC%20to%20provide%20the%20land.%20While%20we%20provided%20the%20wet%20waste%20and%20raised%20funds%2C%20BMC%20provided%20the%20land%20and%20technical%20support.%20Since%20the%20plant%20requires%20one%20ton%20waste%2C%20we%20asked%20nearby%20restaurants%20to%20give%20their%20wet%20waste%2C%20as%20residents%20could%20produce%20only%20680-690%20kg%20per%20day%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0After%20running%20the%20plant%20successfully%20for%20three%20years%2C%20PHRA%20handed%20over%20the%20plant%20to%20BMC%20in%202021%2C%20as%20per%20mutual%20agreement%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20stellar%20transformation%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPHRA%20has%20scaled%20up%20their%20security%20too%2C%20in%20association%20with%20Khar%20police%2C%20say%20members.%20%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20security%20guards%2C%20we%20also%20have%2019%20high-definition%20night%20vision%20security%20cameras%20on%20our%20roads%2C%20which%20can%20even%20read%20a%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20number.%20They%20are%20monitored%20by%20Khar%20police%20station%2C%E2%80%9D%20reveals%20Sonu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20housekeeping%20team%20keeps%20the%20roads%20clean%20through%20regular%20sweeping%2C%20maintains%20the%20flower%20beds%20and%20saplings%20plan