20that%20women%20face%20significant%20challenges%20when%20visiting%20hospitals%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F72679%2Fcare-nx-doorstep-diagnosis-innovative-technology-pregnancy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantenatal%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20long%20travel%20times%20and%20waiting%20periods%20of%20five%20to%20six%20hours%20for%20a%20short%20consultation%20lead%20many%20women%20to%20avoid%20these%20visits%20and%20postpone%20them%20to%20the%20next%20month.%20However%2C%20this%20delay%20prevents%20potential%20risks%20from%20being%20assessed%20in%20a%20timely%20manner.%20I%20became%20aware%20of%20the%20alarming%20mortality%20rates%20among%20tribal%20and%20rural%20pregnant%20women%20and%20felt%20determined%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20after%20creating%20a%20simple%20device%20for%20his%20sister%2C%20Senthil%20felt%20inspired%20to%20assist%20more%20women%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20rural%20and%20remote%20areas.%20His%20aim%20was%20to%20help%20them%20monitor%20essential%20vitals%20usually%20recorded%20during%20antenatal%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20years%20of%20clinical%20trials%2C%20he%20founded%20JioVio%20Healthcare%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMonitoring%20vitals%20in%20a%20single%20device%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20process%20of%20reaching%20out%20to%20rural%20women%2C%20Senthil%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20with%20the%20state%20governments.%20After%20contacting%20them%2C%20the%20secretaries%20inform%20us%20about%20the%20districts%20with%20high%20maternal%20mortality.%20We%20then%20approach%20the%20district%20collector%2C%20who%20onboards%20block-level%20officers%2C%20healthcare%20workers%2C%20and%20rural%20women.%20When%20any%20of%20the%20rural%20women%20get%20pregnant%2C%20a%20mobile%20application%20is%20used%20to%20track%20their%20health%20and%20conduct%20monthly%20checkups.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1-1690550129.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senthil%20felt%20inspired%20to%20assist%20more%20women%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20rural%20and%20remote%20areas.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1-1690550129.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1-1690550129-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1-1690550129-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1-1690550129-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1-1690550129-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325679%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESenthil%20felt%20inspired%20to%20assist%20more%20women%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20rural%20and%20remote%20areas.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20give%20our%20medical%20device%20called%20AlloTricorder%20to%20healthcare%20workers.%20They%20use%20it%20to%20measure%20vital%20parameters%20like%20blood%20pressure%2C%20blood%20glucose%2C%20ECG%2C%20and%20temperature%20%E2%80%94%20all%20using%20a%20single%20device.%20They%20then%20digitally%20transfer%20the%20data%20via%20Bluetooth%20to%20the%20application%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20data%20collected%20at%20hospitals%20is%20the%20same%20as%20what%20we%20capture%20at%20home.%20Our%20idea%20was%20to%20gather%20this%20data%20right%20at%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20home.%20If%20lab%20tests%20are%20necessary%2C%20we%20collect%20the%20sample