ed%20that%20time%20to%20study%20for%20the%20board%20exams.%20But%20not%20Bhagyashree%20Bhansali.%20She%20went%20and%20joined%20the%202011%20anti-corruption%20movement%20launched%20by%20activist%20Anna%20Hazare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20devoted%20her%20college%20life%20to%20addressing%20public%20grievances.%20While%20pursuing%20her%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20in%20business%20administration%2C%20she%20joined%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20advisory%20team.%20She%20focused%20on%20environmental%20issues%20such%20as%20air%20and%20water%20pollution%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323755%2Fmothers-anupama-charulatha-swmrt-bengaluru-plastic-free-low-waste-wedding-composting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emunicipal%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20biodiversity%20loss%2C%20which%20have%20been%20persistent%20challenges%20for%20the%20capital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20work%20involved%20thinking%20of%20different%20ways%20to%20manage%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20waste%2C%20which%20led%20her%20to%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20garbage%20dump%20yards%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20facing%20health%20issues%20due%20to%20environmental%20pollution.%20We%20would%20make%20multiple%20visits%20to%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20and%20seeing%20its%20condition%20just%20shook%20me.%20I%20was%20frustrated%20seeing%20the%20sheer%20number%20of%20plastic%20bottles%20and%20chip%20packets%20there%3B%20the%20amount%20of%20plastic%20waste%20there%20was%20humongous%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhagyashree%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20has%2078%20lakh%20MT%20of%20waste%20and%20reached%20its%20saturation%20point%20in%202002.%20Yet%2C%20700%20MT%20of%20waste%20is%20dumped%20there