%20business%20from%20Tirupati%2C%20who%20recalls%20having%20to%20jump%20through%20hoops%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296115%2Fteenagers-startup-finance4teens-educate-kids-globally-on-banking-financial-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eget%20a%20loan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20run%20a%20milk%20shop%20and%20needed%20a%20loan%20to%20expand.%20I%20had%20to%20make%20multiple%20visits%20to%20get%20my%20loan%20sanctioned%20earlier.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20there%20is%20a%20large%20gender%20gap%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20access%20to%20credit.%20A%202022%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EInternational%20Finance%20Corporation%20(IFC)%20%3C%2Fem%3Eestimates%20a%20Rs%20836%20billion%20credit%20demand%20by%20women-owned%20very%20small%20enterprises.%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3EProtium%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereport%20further%20states%20that%20there%20is%20a%C2%A0%20credit%20gap%20of%20%24158%20billion%20for%20women-led%20businesses%20as%20a%20whole.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20women%20like%20Barathi%20and%20Priya%2C%20India%20P2P%2C%20a%20peer-to-peer%20lending%20platform%20run%20by%20Mumbai-based%20entrepreneur%20Neha%20Juneja%20has%20been%20a%20boon.%20Barathi%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20received%20a%20pamphlet%20and%20I%20called%20them.%20An%20officer%20came%2C%20and%20after%20verifying%20the%20details%2C%20the%20loan%20was%20disbursed%20in%20a%20day.%E2%80%9D%20Similar%20was%20the%20case%20of%20Priya%2C%20who%20availed%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2030%2C000%20in%20March%202023%2C%20and%20was%20successfully%20able%20to%20set%20up%20her%20flower%20shop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%20says%20that%20her%20introduction%20to%20microfinance%20happened%20when%20she%20was%20working%20with%20rural%20women%20at%20Greenway%20Grameen%20Infra%2C%20which%20manufactures%20biomass%20cook%20stoves.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20travelled%20to%20several%20villages%20and%20saw%20the%20thriving%20self-help%2